.TH STOP-COMICOFTHEDAY 1 "May 2026" "Comic of the Day 1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
stop-comicoftheday \- stop the Comic of the Day web application
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B stop-comicoftheday.sh
.SH DESCRIPTION
Finds the running \fBcomicoftheday\fR process by name and sends it \fBSIGTERM\fR.
Also removes any leftover \fI.tmp\fR files from the cache directory.
If no matching process is found, exits cleanly with a message.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Process stopped successfully, or no process was running.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I cache/*.tmp
Partial cache write files. Removed on stop.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR start-comicoftheday (1)
